<h1 local-id=3D"f2c782934528" id=3D"PerformanceReviewSummary-DanteCaranto-O=
verallsummary">Overall summary</h1>
<p local-id=3D"ede268d9dd82">Dante delivered strong performance through a c=
ombination of high-volume execution, technical precision, and proactive tea=
m enablement. His work improved the quality and consistency of customer-fac=
ing API documentation, supported important product initiatives, and strengt=
hened internal documentation practices through reusable process guidance an=
d structured knowledge transfer. He demonstrated clear value not only as an=
 individual contributor, but also as a force multiplier for the broader doc=
umentation team.</p>
<div class=3D"confluence-information-macro confluence-information-macro-inf=
ormation">
<span class=3D"aui-icon aui-icon-small aui-iconfont-info confluence-informa=
tion-macro-icon"></span>
<div class=3D"confluence-information-macro-body">
